s infrastructure, training programs, and a culture that promotes athletic excellence, play a crucial role in Olympic success.\", \"from\": 3362, \"to\": 3579, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This discrepancy\", \"from\": 3362, \"to\": 3378}, {\"ngram\": \"factors\", \"from\": 3395, \"to\": 3402}, {\"ngram\": \"population size\", \"from\": 3410, \"to\": 3425}, {\"ngram\": \"investment\", \"from\": 3435, \"to\": 3445}, {\"ngram\": \"sports infrastructure\", \"from\": 3449, \"to\": 3470}, {\"ngram\": \"training programs\", \"from\": 3472, \"to\": 3489}, {\"ngram\": \"a culture\", \"from\": 3495, \"to\": 3504}, {\"ngram\": \"athletic excellence\", \"from\": 3519, \"to\": 3538}, {\"ngram\": \"a crucial role\", \"from\": 3545, \"to\": 3559}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic success\", \"from\": 3563, \"to\": 3578}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The US has athletes who receive superior training.\", \"from\": 3581, \"to\": 3631, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3585, \"end\": 3587, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999996636329909, \"rank\": 3.363616873739827e-07, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 3592, \"to\": 3600}, {\"ngram\": \"superior training\", \"from\": 3613, \"to\": 3630}]}, {\"sentence\": \"No matter where you are born in the world, if you wanted to be an Olympic swimmer or runner, you would choose the USA for your training over Bangladesh or Indonesia.\", \"from\": 3632, \"to\": 3797, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3746, \"end\": 3749, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.8052240485106718, \"rank\": 0.24189026477157788, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbp